column4: Russia resorted to firing TOS-1 thermobaric weapons into the town to destroy Ukrainian positions. TOS-1 is a short-range multiple rocket launch system that fires thermobaric weapons designed to destroy buildings and fortifications. These weapons are vulnerable to counter-battery fire due to their short range. Beyond Pisky
